3
00:01:54.310 --> 00:02:00.890
Luffy and Robin needed to recover, so the Going Merry
remained anchored off the uninhabited island for four days.

4
00:02:00.890 --> 00:02:05.850
After that, we set sail, and now this is
the third morning since we resumed our voyage.

5
00:02:05.850 --> 00:02:08.690
Today's weather is a gorgeous mix of spring...

6
00:02:09.610 --> 00:02:11.310
and occasional bouts of summer.

7
00:02:16.700 --> 00:02:18.490
What a beautiful day!

8
