10
00:02:32.420 --> 00:02:34.100
Mmm, it's delicious!

11
00:02:34.100 --> 00:02:36.680
I'm overjoyed!

12
00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:39.470
Keep it down! I'm trying to sleep!

13
00:02:39.470 --> 00:02:43.000
Yeah, yeah... Sorry about that, cactus head.

14
00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:45.310
What'd you say, dartboard brows?!

15
00:02:45.310 --> 00:02:47.950
Dar– Did I hear you right, you bastard?!

16
00:02:47.950 --> 00:02:50.000
Dartboard brows.

17
00:02:53.640 --> 00:02:57.610
Luffy! Yeah! Luffy! All right!

18
00:02:57.610 --> 00:03:02.230
Luffy! Yeah! Luffy!

19
00:03:04.430 --> 00:03:06.980
Finally!

20
00:03:05.640 --> 00:03:06.980
Luffy!

21
00:03:13.790 --> 00:03:16.750
This is my frozen-self reenactment.

22
00:03:23.720 --> 00:03:27.890
The heck...? I can't believe he's doing that
after he got frozen and almost died.

23
00:03:29.740 --> 00:03:30.730
Was it close?

24
00:03:30.730 --> 00:03:33.480
You nailed it! That was exactly it, Luffy!

25
00:03:33.480 --> 00:03:35.870
Clean that up good, okay, Luffy?!

26
00:03:35.870 --> 00:03:38.860
Hm...? Oh! What're you eating, Nami?

27
00:03:38.860 --> 00:03:41.140
It's paille, a potato dish.

28
00:03:41.940 --> 00:03:45.240
Potato, huh? I'm hungry too. Hey, Sanji!

29
00:03:45.240 --> 00:03:48.960
Just how much sleep do you need anyway?!

30
00:03:48.960 --> 00:03:52.210
How much sleep I "need" is
 my business! Let's settle this!

31
00:04:03.590 --> 00:04:06.300
They said this is called paille. It's good!

32
00:04:06.300 --> 00:04:08.580
What's paille?

33
00:04:08.580 --> 00:04:12.650
It's the tail meat of a huge
monster named Paille.

34
00:04:12.650 --> 00:04:16.190
I slew it, though. It was at least
a hundred meters tall.

35
00:04:16.800 --> 00:04:19.460
A hundred meters?! That's amazing, Usopp!

36
00:04:19.460 --> 00:04:21.610
Yeah, and I did it all before breakfast.

37
00:04:21.610 --> 00:04:24.260
What? You got up early and killed it?

38
00:04:24.260 --> 00:04:27.490
Chopper, say my name.

39
00:04:27.490 --> 00:04:31.080
What? That's, of course, C-Captain...

40
00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:35.580
That's right! My name is Captain... Usopp–

41
00:04:37.420 --> 00:04:39.340
Robin!

42
00:04:39.340 --> 00:04:42.500
Hey! Robin my love!

43
00:04:42.500 --> 00:04:43.720
Robin!

44
00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:46.510
How are you feeling? Are you chilly?

45
00:04:46.510 --> 00:04:50.970
I'm feeling a lot better
all thanks to an amazing doctor.

46
00:04:50.970 --> 00:04:56.600
Oh, being called an amazing doctor won't
make me feel happy or anything, you jerk.

47
00:04:56.600 --> 00:04:58.440
He sure does look happy.

48
00:04:57.560 --> 00:04:58.440
Yeah.

49
00:04:58.440 --> 00:05:00.270
Take it easy, Robin.

50
00:05:00.270 --> 00:05:05.170
Don't feel pressured just because Luffy is up
and about after experiencing the same thing.

51
00:05:05.170 --> 00:05:07.160
It's okay to take your time and rest.

52
00:05:07.160 --> 00:05:09.160
– Yay! 
– That wasn't a compliement!

