60
00:05:46.070 --> 00:05:50.260
Anyway, this paille thing is so good
that we can't stop eating it.

61
00:05:50.260 --> 00:05:52.000
Yeah, it's yummy!

62
00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:54.040
