It went to your side, so take a look!

67
00:06:01.480 --> 00:06:02.380
Is that true?

68
00:06:02.380 --> 00:06:04.380
A frog...? Could it be that frog?

69
00:06:04.380 --> 00:06:09.470
Hey, Luffy, are you seriously taking stock
in what that dumb admiral said?

70
00:06:09.470 --> 00:06:11.550
For starters, a frog could never do the–

