81
00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:39.960
It feels like the ship changed course.

82
00:06:39.960 --> 00:06:44.420
Hey, you guys! Who said you could
change course without consulting me?!

83
00:06:44.420 --> 00:06:46.650
Hey, Nami, you've got to hear this!

84
00:06:46.650 --> 00:06:49.380
We found a huge frog
with scars all over its body!

85
00:06:50.100 --> 00:06:51.680
What the heck?

86
00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:55.240
The plan's to roast it whole and eat it!

87
00:06:55.240 --> 00:06:56.470
